QtJambiInterface
public class QResizeEvent
extends QEvent

The QResizeEvent class contains event parameters for resize events. Resize events are sent to widgets that have been resized.

The event handler QWidget::resizeEvent() receives resize events.

See also:
QWidget::resize(), and QWidget::setGeometry().
